t: Q: How do you fold up the ab lounge ultra
s: To fold the Ab Lounge Ultra for storage, you'll first detach the two elastic bands from the bottom of the frame support. Then, remove the black Locking Knob found on the side of the frame (this unlocks the support bar). Now you're able to fold the unit - it collapses to under 5" in width.
